lycanthropy-heal-allies-name = Heal allies
lycanthropy-heal-allies-desc = Gain the ability to heal all other werewolves within range.

lycanthropy-steel-claws-name = Steel claws
lycanthropy-steel-claws-desc = Your claws become razor-sharp, increasing the damage of your attacks.

lycanthropy-long-jump-name = Long lunge
lycanthropy-long-jump-desc = Your lunges become longer.

lycanthropy-thick-fur-name = Thick fur
lycanthropy-thick-fur-desc = Your thick fur allows you to increase your health.

lycanthropy-stone-claws-name = Stonecutting claws
lycanthropy-stone-claws-desc = Your claws become so durable that they allow you to smash through any obstacles.

lycanthropy-regen-name = Regeneration
lycanthropy-regen-desc = Gain the ability to restore a portion of your health.

lycanthropy-blood-feel-name = Blood sense
lycanthropy-blood-feel-desc = Gain the ability to track your victims by the scent of blood.

lycanthropy-hot-blood-name = Hot blood
lycanthropy-hot-blood-desc = Gain the ability to increase your speed for a short time.

lycanthropy-shadow-dash-name = Shadow lunge
lycanthropy-shadow-dash-desc = Gain the ability to stun your target when lunging.

lycanthropy-blood-hunt-name = Blood hunt
lycanthropy-blood-hunt-desc = Gain the ability to enter hunting mode, removing stamina damage from lunges in exchange for some health damage.

lycanthropy-rage-name = Lunar rage
lycanthropy-rage-desc = Gain the ability to ignore incoming stamina damage and receive a slight speed boost for several seconds.

lycanthropy-tearing-name = Rending maw
lycanthropy-tearing-desc = Gain the ability to attack with your maw, dealing massive damage.

lycanthropy-morph-name = Transformation
lycanthropy-morph-desc = Gain the ability to transform into a werewolf and back at any time.